        "title": "IN THE CELLAR",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>Only the best-quality, free-run juice is used to produce this unique Sauvignon Blanc wine. An intriguing blend of barrel-matured and fresh, crisp, tank-fermented Sauvignon Blanc, approximately 25% of this wine was wild-yeast fermented, before being aged in older French oak barrels to provide complexity and depth of flavour. The remainder of the wine was fermented in stainless steel tanks, highlighting the wonderful, primary-fruit character of this vintage.</p>",
